E(Y^2) = n(n-1) (1 - 2/n)^k + n (1 - 1/n)^k
\text{Var}(Y) = E(Y^2) - E(Y)^2 = n(n-1)(1 - 2/n)^k + n (1 - 1/n)^k - n^2 (1 - 1/n)^{2k}
